 completion tool technology that offers remote signaling capabilities for valves and sleeves for a variety of applications and completion designs and • german oil tools – a line of advanced liner hanger systems and other completion tool technologies products and accessories “we are proud to unveil this meaningful expansion to our portfolio of leadingedge completion tool technologies” commented clay williams nov chairman president and ceo “nov now offers a comprehensive set of differentiated completion tool products and solutions that we believe address the most pressing needs within the global marketplace” read the full news release here visit our completion tools section for more information published date  source national oilwell varco news a lighter load for the uks largest warships … read full article nov today episode   inspirational leadership join nov’s chief marketing officer david reid as he sits down with host michael gaines in this first episode of nov’s new podcast series nov today in this episode david and michael discuss inspirational leadership and how failure can propel individuals and companies to achieve greater heights of future success… read full article nov’s stickslip mitigation system featured in june offshore engineer … read full article search locations segments rig systemswellbore technologiescompletion  production solutions social media national oilwell varco national oilwell varco search regions mynov homenews and eventsnewsnov expands completion tool technology product offering nov expands completion tool technology product offering houstonbusiness wirejun   national oilwell varco inc nyse nov announced today the introduction of several new proprietary technologies to its completion tools portfolio • bulldog frac™  a slidingsleeve annular fracturing system that provides pinpoint accuracy zonal isolation and improved reliability • bullmastiff™  a balldrop openhole slidingsleeve sand control fracturing system • rottweiler™  a product famil