employees  sector oil  gas productsservices sales or revenue  b industry companies on the energy service y sales change  fiscal year ends december  download reports description national oilwell varco inc national oilwell varco inc provides equipment and components that are used in oil and gas drilling and production operations oilfield services and supply chain integration services to the upstream oil and gas industry the company operates through the following segments rig systems rig aftermarket wellbore technologies and completion and production solutions the rig systems segment designs manufactures and sells land rigs offshore drilling equipment packages including installation and commissioning services and drilling rig components that mechanize and automate the drilling process and rig functionality the rig aftermarket segment provides spare parts repair and rentals as well as technical support field service and first well support field engineering and customer training the wellbore technologies segment designs manufactures rents and sells a variety of equipment and technologies used to perform drilling operations and offers services that optimize their performance the completion and production solutions segment integrates technologies for well completions and oil and gas production the company was founded in  and is headquartered in houston tx expand key people national oilwell varco inc board of directors nametitle current board membership clay c williams  chairman president  chief executive officer national oilwell varco inc benchmark electronics inc sam houston area council james t hackett  independent nonexecutive director national oilwell varco inc greg l armstrong  lead independent nonexecutive director national oilwell varco inc william r thomas  independent nonemployee director national oilwell varco inc marcela e donadio  independent nonemployee director national oilwell varco inc david d harrison  independent nonemployee director national oilwell varc